{"tid":2112892,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"走投無路 求認真意見","createTime":"2020-07-17T16:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T09:09:40.000Z","uid":61825,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"53b4274a264c95df61cb5ea834df3950e784e15f","tid":2112892,"uid":61825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T16:22:58.000Z","msg":"本身爭緊出面大概廿萬<br />\n哩幾個月失業開始還唔起財仔<br />\n想問下大家如果冇入息，有冇方法仲借到錢<br />\n只想捱過哩一兩個月搵到工<br />\n<br />\n另外，想問下破產大概要幾多錢？<br />\n我真係好唔想死，求方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab56abc64b18204e88230b500b00977f6c67ed30","tid":2112892,"uid":268625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T16:23:52.000Z","msg":"債務重組？"},{"pid":"eab9bd127e534781cac58ad2628deed8f1e2a3c4","tid":2112892,"uid":29093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">又一個爛賭鬼</span></strong>"},{"pid":"d125cb51cdd9783f25268776bfa45207f4b4fdb3","tid":2112892,"uid":127007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T16:24:31.000Z","msg":"本身做乜 有幾錢收入"},{"pid":"94bb07fb061cdbdffc1eb96dfbe724fb9e1807f9","tid":2112892,"uid":4740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T16:25:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8d23aa5732d7ed1f7e7be010a8254009c08ffd4","tid":2112892,"uid":78492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T16:31:08.000Z","msg":"起一起樓主底，又賭，又煙。<br />\n點解有負債都仲要食煙<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上【破產討論區】問人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd3c7b30ad06dee164a1a76c051e003d934484d","tid":2112892,"uid":12463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T16:32:45.000Z","msg":"冇做ptbf？"},{"pid":"63b873304f1e0726cb497c63bdd7e07f562ae7b5